content: How do l access discord from my computer instead of my phone

Hi <@1287103049600598166> you can download the Discord app from the official website https://discord.com/download Once you have that installed you'll need to log in using the same user name and password you use to sign into the Discord app on your phone to see your favourite Discord server.

Hi <@1287103049600598166> you can open any browser and go to discord.com and log in. 
Or you can follow Midsummer's instructions and download the app.
